25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：在学习 AD 域环境攻击面和横向移动路径的安全研究者。\n阅读前提：理解 Kerberos、域控、用户组与基本 Windows 管理概念。\n核心收获：把枚举、路径分析、凭据利用与横向移动串联起来。\n说明：AD 组件版本和补丁状态会影响具体利用路径。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Active Directory（AD）是企业网络的核心基础设施，管理着组织中的用户、计算机、权限和策略。对于渗透测试人员而言，攻破域环境意味着能够控制整个企业网络。本文将从 AD 基础概念入手，系统讲解域环境信息收集、Kerberos 认证攻击、横向移动技术以及常见的域攻击手法，包括 Pass-the-Hash、Kerberoasting 等核心技术。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"active-directory-核心概念","children":["Active Directory 核心概念",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#active-directory-核心概念","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"域domain与域控制器domain-controller","children":["域（Domain）与域控制器（Domain Controller）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#域domain与域控制器domain-controller","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"域是 Active Directory 的基本管理单元，域控制器（DC）是运行 AD DS 服务的 Windows Server，负责存储目录数据库（NTDS.dit）并处理所有认证请求。"}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"组织单位ou与组策略gpo","children":["组织单位（OU）与组策略（GPO）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#组织单位ou与组策略gpo","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"OU 是 AD 中用于组织和管理对象的容器，GPO 则通过链接到 OU 来下发安全策略和配置。"}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"关键-ad-对象","children":["关键 AD 对象",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#关键-ad-对象","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"对象类型"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"说明"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"渗透测试关注点"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"用户账户"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"域用户"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"弱密码、SPN 设置、特权组成员"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"计算机账户"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"域内机器"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"不受约束的委派"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"服务账户"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"运行服务的账户"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Kerberoasting 目标"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"组"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"安全组/分发组"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Domain Admins、Enterprise Admins"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"GPO"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"组策略对象"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"密码策略、脚本执行"}]]}]]}]]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"域环境信息收集","children":["域环境信息收集",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#域环境信息收集","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"bloodhound","children":["BloodHound",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#bloodhound","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"BloodHound 是域渗透中最强大的信息收集和攻击路径分析工具，通过图数据库可视化展示域内的权限关系。"}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h4",null,{"id":"数据收集--sharphound","children":["数据收集 — SharpHound",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#数据收集--sharphound","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L33","\n",["$","h4",null,{"id":"bloodhound-攻击路径分析","children":["BloodHound 攻击路径分析",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#bloodhound-攻击路径分析","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在 BloodHound 中导入数据后，可以使用内置查询发现攻击路径："}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Find Shortest Paths to Domain Admins"}]," — 查找到域管理员的最短攻击路径"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Find Principals with DCSync Rights"}]," — 查找具有 DCSync 权限的主体"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[[